# FLA-parity evaluation harness — local working copy only (configs/launchers/
# logs/summaries used to iterate on the 300M & 1B comparison runs; not part
# of the Primus public surface, kept on disk for follow-up work).
/eval/

# Pre-push FLA parity sanity harness — local-only (configs/driver/logs used to
# re-verify all 5 models match FLA speed + loss before pushing).
/sanity_before_push/

# Experiment-only model config: FLA-exact mamba2 replica used to prove the
# 300M mamba_hybrid loss offset is architecture (not a bug). Not a production
# model — delete or keep local; never merge.
/primus/configs/models/megatron/zebra_llama_300M_mamba_hybrid_flaexact.yaml

